high_descs: Turn around and go to the round dining table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the table.
Turn to the left and go to the wall, hang a right and go to the dining table where the tomatoes are.
Cut the tomato farthest from you into slices.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn around, go to the wall, hang a right and go to the dining table where the tomatoes are.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge and close the door, remove the tomato from the fridge once it is cold.
Turn to the left, go to the wall, turn to the left and go to the dining table.
Put the tomato on the table to the left of the salt and pepper.
anns.task_desc: Put cold tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the round black table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the table.
Turn left and walk to the right to the round table.
Slice the tomato the the left of the plant on the table.
Turn right and walk to the white fridge on the left.
Put the knife inside the fridge on the shelf in the middle to chill and close the door.
Turn around and walk right to the side of the round table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on the left.
Put the slice of tomato inside the fridge on the left side of the shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the left side of the round table.
Put the chilled slice of tomato to the left of the gold pepper grinders on the table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a knife and place a chilled slice of tomato on a table.
